  "rationale": "Single sanctioned opening bookend re-expressed on the ALIGNMENT axis only: the seeded centered display-over-staggered-media becomes the brand's left-anchored interlock. A long didone display STATEMENT ('WOODWAVE GALLERY') wraps around ONE landscape hero photograph floated right (float-wrap + inset register the image edge to the text block so nothing free-floats), with the measured eyebrow split into a two-line tracked caption pinned top-left. Dark inverse surface carries the page's single gold accent on the display title only; measured support line and typographic 'Buy Tickets' link (no button, per neverDo) preserve the original copy verbatim. novelty:'adapt', seededFrom the project hero pattern; palette/type tiers/spacing identical to the seed."
